{"slug":{"en":"budgeting"},"projectTitle":{"en":"The Visual Budgeting App","ja":"ビジュアル予算作成アプリ"},"date":{"en":"February 21, 2020","ja":"2020年2月21日"},"featureImage":{"en":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"p0ly3e00wdqi"}},"id":"5cRRI0fbn3IKZbIxvQSBsE","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-11T03:21:43.782Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-11T03:21:43.782Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Visual Budgeting App Feature Image"},"file":{"en":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/p0ly3e00wdqi/5cRRI0fbn3IKZbIxvQSBsE/afc7d79da83de87df25def381cc29b1a/visual-finance-feature.png","details":{"size":46850,"image":{"width":544,"height":240}},"fileName":"visual-finance-feature.png","contentType":"image/png"}}}}},"projectContent":{"en":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"About","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"The Visual Budgeting App is an idea for a mobile application that helps users grow their finances based on visual insights from their daily, weekly, and monthly spending habits. The app first asks users their financial goals and income, then dynamically guides users towards those goals. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"UX Methods Used","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Sketch","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Personas","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Wireframes","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"User flows","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"High-fidelity mockups","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"}],"nodeType":"unordered-list"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Design Tools","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Sketch","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Pen & Paper","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"}],"nodeType":"unordered-list"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Process","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Define Phase","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Requirements Brainstorming","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-4"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"To start off the project, we brainstorm feel, features, and usage characteristics for the app. Narrowing down the problems you wish to solve allows you to focus on solving the users' needs.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"p0ly3e00wdqi"}},"id":"7KujZfkYFtHDtQFrOKTWNf","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-11T01:37:59.713Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-11T01:37:59.713Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Tidy Life Brainstorming"},"file":{"en":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/p0ly3e00wdqi/7KujZfkYFtHDtQFrOKTWNf/dddd54a79ff84126a2e9f5aeaaf437d4/tidylife-wireframe-1.jpg","details":{"size":150305,"image":{"width":1200,"height":707}},"fileName":"tidylife-wireframe-1.jpg","contentType":"image/jpeg"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"p0ly3e00wdqi"}},"id":"1hYvmItL7pDA0EmGKprbxJ","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-11T01:39:10.987Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-11T01:39:10.987Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Tidy Finance Brainstorming Financial Decisions"},"file":{"en":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/p0ly3e00wdqi/1hYvmItL7pDA0EmGKprbxJ/088e99385288134b81d9852bf0c5c51c/tidylife-wireframe-2.jpg","details":{"size":277363,"image":{"width":1200,"height":894}},"fileName":"tidylife-wireframe-2.jpg","contentType":"image/jpeg"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"One important feature from brainstorming appeared: separating cash from card expenses, but listing them side by side. This helps the user balance cash and card spending visually, perhaps even psychologically.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Discover Phase","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Persona","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-4"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"What kind of users find value from our app? What are their goals and frustrations? In order to understand what problem the Visual Budgeting App would solve, we needed to first understand our target user. Personas help us empathize with a particular user segment's needs. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"p0ly3e00wdqi"}},"id":"PX4b1Sir8F0phdSyHF55B","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-11T01:38:34.844Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-11T01:38:34.844Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Tidy Finance Personas"},"file":{"en":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/p0ly3e00wdqi/PX4b1Sir8F0phdSyHF55B/f40301b11ee6bf1f10d9a8964521b786/tidy-finance-persona.png","details":{"size":529985,"image":{"width":1024,"height":619}},"fileName":"tidy-finance-persona.png","contentType":"image/png"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Design Phase","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Wireframes & Userflows","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-4"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"With the target user's goals in mind, we can create wireframes and user flows.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"The key benefit of the app is the ability to visualize their daily, weekly, and monthly budget progress. Therefore, the home screen will focus on delivering this value.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Home screen initial concept","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-4"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"p0ly3e00wdqi"}},"id":"7GJMwdDItRhUPDGrPNeJKL","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-11T01:40:42.548Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-11T01:40:42.548Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Tidy Life Wireframes Time Frame"},"file":{"en":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/p0ly3e00wdqi/7GJMwdDItRhUPDGrPNeJKL/37cb871014b6f0820236f5ccd04c2107/tidylife-wireframe-3-1.jpg","details":{"size":227331,"image":{"width":1200,"height":727}},"fileName":"tidylife-wireframe-3-1.jpg","contentType":"image/jpeg"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"The home screen is simple. It only has one purpose: to let the user know how much left they have in their daily/weekly/monthly budget. The entire screen acts as a visual water level showing the percentage/amount of money spent and the percentage/amount of money left.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Inputting expenses concept","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-4"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Inputting daily cash expenses into the app is likely the biggest obstacle we face in terms of retention (credit expenses would be automatically synced with an account). Because of this, the app must have an extremely simple UI. You can see examples of this in some key design decisions:","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"There are only 5 tabs in the bottom navigation, and they are always visible.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"A giant 'add expense' button is in the center of the bottom navigation.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"}],"nodeType":"unordered-list"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"p0ly3e00wdqi"}},"id":"7dQbOcpe7jNo8GtHNdvO4z","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-11T01:41:23.061Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-11T01:41:23.061Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Tidy Finance Wireframes Input Expense User Flow"},"file":{"en":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/p0ly3e00wdqi/7dQbOcpe7jNo8GtHNdvO4z/d72045947f85f29543b16a054e720623/tidylife-input-expense-userflow.png.jpg","details":{"size":246381,"image":{"width":1200,"height":908}},"fileName":"tidylife-input-expense-userflow.png.jpg","contentType":"image/jpeg"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Only those steps giving valuable information to the user to minimize steps.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Once an expense is inputted, the user can instantly verify it at the bottom of the screen. A list of today's expenses will be shown. From this list, the user can view, edit, or delete each daily expense.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Checking expenses concept","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-4"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"The user can check expenses from the second icon in the main navigation (shown below). When tapped, the screen will change to today's expenses list. From here, the user can view, edit, or delete expenses.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"p0ly3e00wdqi"}},"id":"3lAcJkaujaG2jSqsbkiDcC","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-11T01:38:20.280Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-11T01:38:20.280Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Tidy Life Check Expenses User Flow"},"file":{"en":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/p0ly3e00wdqi/3lAcJkaujaG2jSqsbkiDcC/9f3355d353780d566b90d61e7e9a6086/tidylife-check-expenses-userflow.jpg","details":{"size":198019,"image":{"width":1200,"height":812}},"fileName":"tidylife-check-expenses-userflow.jpg","contentType":"image/jpeg"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"The user can also navigate to weekly, monthly, or yearly expense lists via a link in the top left corner of the screen. From there, the user can dive down into specific days, weeks, months that they want to see.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Hi-fidelity Mockups","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Once the main structure of the app is decided, we can create hi-fidelity mockups in order to guide the developer in app creation.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Home screen","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-4"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"p0ly3e00wdqi"}},"id":"38fIdgZg8AXA0lXnhIeVPA","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-11T01:40:11.159Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-11T01:40:11.159Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Tidy Finance HiFi Mockups Home Levels"},"file":{"en":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/p0ly3e00wdqi/38fIdgZg8AXA0lXnhIeVPA/852c6d8f5655b795a78e683b584698a7/tidyfinance-home-levels.png","details":{"size":361512,"image":{"width":2104,"height":1107}},"fileName":"tidyfinance-home-levels.png","contentType":"image/png"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Showing the amount of budget left","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\nThe home screen changes dynamically depending on how much daily/weekly/monthly budget the user has left. The following mockups show different levels of money left in a January budget of ¥120000.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\n","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"The use of color","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"You'll notice that color is now a key method of communication. The actual color choice came through many iterations. We can not depend on color as the only expression of visualized data because some people have a red-green color blind deficiency. This is why color is used together with a filled area to express the amount of budget left.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"p0ly3e00wdqi"}},"id":"2JJlMwcJw3S54MZGawQAqL","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-11T01:41:52.707Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-11T01:41:52.707Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Tidy Finance HiFi Mockup Home Screen"},"file":{"en":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/p0ly3e00wdqi/2JJlMwcJw3S54MZGawQAqL/a09353932f57fb00a18bb46cfd2da95f/tidyfinance-home-time-1.png","details":{"size":214969,"image":{"width":2104,"height":1107}},"fileName":"tidyfinance-home-time-1.png","contentType":"image/png"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Switching between monthly/weekly/daily budgets","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\nThe user can tap the icons in the upper right-hand corner to switch between monthly, weekly and daily budgets. This feature is to help the user make better financial decisions dynamically. The following mockups show this function.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Expenses screen","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-4"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"p0ly3e00wdqi"}},"id":"17FtuVfDhk2MP8q1hcJWks","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-11T01:39:45.571Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-11T01:39:45.571Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Tidy Life HiFi Mockup Time Period"},"file":{"en":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/p0ly3e00wdqi/17FtuVfDhk2MP8q1hcJWks/7cb6e1a8f6bae795195a06e98e9cb617/tidyfinance-expenses.png","details":{"size":325680,"image":{"width":2104,"height":1107}},"fileName":"tidyfinance-expenses.png","contentType":"image/png"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"The main purpose of the expenses screen is to allow users to be transparent with themselves about how they spend money.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Expenses can be viewed on a day-to-day basis, monthly, or yearly. Each group of expenses is automatically totaled, and a left-to-right level is given to aid the user in understanding the percentage of their budget that they spent.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Expenses Input Screen","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-4"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"p0ly3e00wdqi"}},"id":"2MU6AV4Twr7RSzcvY3Vdxq","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-11T01:42:17.533Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-11T01:42:17.533Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Tidy Finance HiFi Mockup Input Expense"},"file":{"en":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/p0ly3e00wdqi/2MU6AV4Twr7RSzcvY3Vdxq/459afc0e6cebc47692a6ecaf3bf93571/tidyfinance-input-expense-2.png","details":{"size":220615,"image":{"width":2104,"height":1107}},"fileName":"tidyfinance-input-expense-2.png","contentType":"image/png"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Users tap the large \"+\" button in the bottom tab to get to the Expenses Input Screen. To input an expense, the user","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Types an expense name","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Types how much it cost","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Taps the category from the category list","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Taps the option for credit or card","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Taps \"Log Expense\"","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"}],"nodeType":"unordered-list"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Once the user inputs an expense, a scrollable list is generated at the bottom of the screen where they can confirm, edit and delete the daily expenses. A totaled progress bar also appears to help them understand the impact on their daily budget.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Less is more","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"The best User Experience is a beautiful magic moment where the user can look at a screen and instantly understand the purpose and how it will add value to their life. When they feel value again and again, they build a habit around the product and integrate it into their lives. This is the goal of every UX Designer.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"While there are many functions that you can integrate into the app, it's more valuable for the user to define a few key features that provide the most value and focus on how you can make those powerful and simple for the user to interact with.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"ja":{"nodeType":"document","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"heading-2","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"プロジェクトについて","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Visual Budgetingアプリは、ユーザーが毎日、毎週、毎月の支出習慣から視覚的な洞察に基づいて財政を成長させるのに役立つモバイルアプリケーションのアイデアです。 このアプリは、最初にユーザーに財務上の目標と収入を尋ね、次に動的にそれらの目標に向かってユーザーを導きます。","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-3","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"UX メソッド","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"unordered-list","content":[{"nodeType":"list-item","content":[{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Sketch","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"list-item","content":[{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"ペルソナ","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"list-item","content":[{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"ワイヤーフレーム","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"list-item","content":[{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"ユーザーフロー","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"list-item","content":[{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"High-fidelity モックアップ","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}}],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-3","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Design ツール","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"unordered-list","content":[{"nodeType":"list-item","content":[{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Sketch","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"list-item","content":[{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"ペンとスケッチパッド","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}}],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-2","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"プロセス","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-3","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"定義段階","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-4","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"要件ブレーンストーミング","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"プロジェクトを開始するには、アプリの感触、機能、使用特性をブレインストーミングします。 解決したい問題を絞り込むことで、ユーザーのニーズの解決に集中できます。","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block","content":[],"data":{"target":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"p0ly3e00wdqi"}},"id":"7KujZfkYFtHDtQFrOKTWNf","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-11T01:37:59.713Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-11T01:37:59.713Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Tidy Life Brainstorming"},"file":{"en":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/p0ly3e00wdqi/7KujZfkYFtHDtQFrOKTWNf/dddd54a79ff84126a2e9f5aeaaf437d4/tidylife-wireframe-1.jpg","details":{"size":150305,"image":{"width":1200,"height":707}},"fileName":"tidylife-wireframe-1.jpg","contentType":"image/jpeg"}}}}}},{"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block","content":[],"data":{"target":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"p0ly3e00wdqi"}},"id":"1hYvmItL7pDA0EmGKprbxJ","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-11T01:39:10.987Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-11T01:39:10.987Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Tidy Finance Brainstorming Financial Decisions"},"file":{"en":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/p0ly3e00wdqi/1hYvmItL7pDA0EmGKprbxJ/088e99385288134b81d9852bf0c5c51c/tidylife-wireframe-2.jpg","details":{"size":277363,"image":{"width":1200,"height":894}},"fileName":"tidylife-wireframe-2.jpg","contentType":"image/jpeg"}}}}}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"ブレーンストーミングのおかげで重要な機能の1つが特に現れました。カードの費用から現金を分離しますが、それらを並べてリストします。 これにより、ユーザーは現金とカードの支出のバランスを視覚的に、おそらくは心理的にも支援します。","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-3","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"発見段階","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-4","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"ペルソナ","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"のようなユーザーが私たちのアプリから価値を見つけますか？ 彼らの目標と不満は何ですか？ Visual Budgetingアプリが解決する問題を理解するために、まずターゲットユーザーを理解する必要があります。 ペルソナは、特定のユーザーセグメントのニーズに共感するのに役立ちます。","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block","content":[],"data":{"target":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"p0ly3e00wdqi"}},"id":"PX4b1Sir8F0phdSyHF55B","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-11T01:38:34.844Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-11T01:38:34.844Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Tidy Finance Personas"},"file":{"en":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/p0ly3e00wdqi/PX4b1Sir8F0phdSyHF55B/f40301b11ee6bf1f10d9a8964521b786/tidy-finance-persona.png","details":{"size":529985,"image":{"width":1024,"height":619}},"fileName":"tidy-finance-persona.png","contentType":"image/png"}}}}}},{"nodeType":"heading-3","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"デザイン段階","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-4","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"ワイヤーフレームとユーザーフロー","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"ターゲットユーザーの目標を念頭に置いて、ワイヤーフレームとユーザーフローを作成できます。","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"アプリの主な利点は、毎日、毎週、毎月の予算の進捗状況を視覚化できることです。 したがって、ホーム画面はこの価値を提供することに焦点を当てます。","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-4","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"ホーム画面の初期コンセプト","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block","content":[],"data":{"target":{"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"p0ly3e00wdqi"}},"id":"7GJMwdDItRhUPDGrPNeJKL","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-06-11T01:40:42.548Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-11T01:40:42.548Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Tidy Life Wireframes Time Frame"},"file":{"en":{"u